    <p id="script">
        The pain started about three days ago.
        At first it was just a dull ache in my lower back,
        but since yesterday it's become much sharper.
        It shoots down my right leg when I try to stand up.
        On a scale of one to ten, it's about a seven when I'm moving,
        but only a three when I'm lying down.
        I've taken paracetamol, but it doesn't seem to help much.
    </p>

    <button onclick="playVoice()">â–¶ Play Audio</button>
